       	       	<div itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/ImageObject" style="display: none">
			<h2 itemprop="name">Packers And Movers in Pune</h2>
			<img src="https://images.jdmagicbox.com/comp/pune/g1/020pxx20.xx20.150123162647.e6g1/catalogue/southern-express-packers-and-movers-transport-nagar-nigdi-pune-packers-and-movers-r0m3m7p8bq.jpg?clr=#29293d" alt="Packers And Movers Pune" itemprop="contentUrl">
		</div>
		<span class="stxt lng_commn_all">
		Packers and movers are equipped to systematically handle the process of shifting, for an office or a house. By deciding to hire packers and movers, you can heave a sigh of relief as their expertise in the field makes the entire process hassle-free. The services offered by these professional companies entail packing, unpacking, loading and unloading of goods and furniture from one location to another within the city or from one city to another. Moving companies that pack and move ensure the safety of your furniture and other goods by making use of packaging material like cardboard boxes, bubble wraps and cling wraps. Fragile goods like glassware as well as electronics are packed and handled with extreme care. Dismantling the furniture at the time of packing and then assembling it while unpacking also falls under their purview. The quotation of the cost that will be incurred is provided by inspecting the quantity and weight of the goods that are to be transported. Please scroll up to find a wide list of all the packers and movers in  Pune.</span> 
	 	</div>
	 	<div class="wrapper essays-section pt-10 pb-10 col-md-12">
		      		<div class="wrapper essays-content ">
					<h3>How can Justdial help in choosing the best Packers and Movers near you?</h3><br>
				 	<p>You can search Packers And Movers in Pune on the basis of your location, popularity, ratings &amp; reviews on Justdial. To get the best offers from business listed with Justdial, click on the Best Deals tab beside listings and fillup the requirements. Businesses will contact with their best offers. You can negotiate with them. You can now chat with businesses and get multiple quotes in a jiffy on the JD Android and iOS app.</p></div></div>		 <div class="wrapper essays-section pt-10 pb-10">
			<div class="col-md-12">
				<h2 class="wrapper essays-heading pt-10 pb-10 text-left">
					Relax and let packers and movers in  Pune help you relocate your office or home
				</h2>
				<div class="wrapper essays-content "><p>Packers and movers are professional service providers who use modern equipment to systematically relocate a house or an office. They provide packing, unpacking, transporting, loading and unloading services required in the shifting of a residential or a commercial place within the city, or between states. You can select from a number of top rated packers and movers in  Pune offering excellent services at competitive prices.</p>
<p></p><h3>Services provided by packers and movers</h3><p></p>
<p>Listed below are the various services provided by packers and movers  Pune has</p>
<p><b>Local and Domestic Shifting</b></p>
<p>Moving or relocating office, residence, showroom or warehouse within city limits, between cities or between states can be done smoothly by availing the services of packers and movers. They hire trained and highly professional people who are experts in dismantling, refitting and shifting services. Fragile goods are packed with extra care to avoid any damages during transit or while the loading and unloading process.</p>
<p><b>International Shifting</b></p>
<p>Several experienced international packers and movers offer seamless international relocation services. They take care of all the procedures required for smooth transition of international relocation services.</p>
<p><b>Corporate Relocation</b></p>
<p>Packing and moving experts analyse the time required to dismantle, pack, load and transport the fixed and variable custom made furniture like work stations, interior partition, servers, data centres, cabins, electrical fittings, etc. and share the same with the company. A team of highly trained professionals work in tandem for the smooth and timely relocation of the corporate office.</p>
<p><b>IT Equipment Relocation</b></p>
<p>In  Pune packers and movers provide unmatched services for relocation of IT equipment like data centres, single or multiple servers, disk arrays, routers and switches, storage racks, rack mounted equipment, etc. High value equipment are packed with custom made special cartons to safeguard them from any damage during the transit.</p>
<p><b>Car and bike carriers</b></p>
<p>Packers and movers have a dedicated team for transporting cars or bikes anywhere across the country. The vehicle to be shifted is safely packed to prevent any damage during the transit or during loading and unloading process.</p>
<p><b>Warehouse Storage</b></p>
<p>At times, a customer cannot get all the goods shifted to the relocated place at once. Professional packers and movers provide warehouse services where a customer can hire a section of the warehouse for long term or short term to store the goods that could not be shifted to the relocated place and have it transported at a later stage.</p>

<p></p><h3>How much do packers and movers charge?</h3><p></p>

<table border="1">
<thead>
<tr><th>Local Shifting</th>
<th>Approximate shifting charges (within 50kms)</th>
</tr></thead>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td>1BHK house shifting</td>
<td>Rs. 3000 - Rs. 10000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2BHK house shifting</td>
<td>Rs. 4000 - Rs. 12000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>3BHK house shifting</td>
<td>Rs. 5000 - Rs. 18000</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>4BHK house shifting</td>
<td>Rs. 8000 - Rs. 28000</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
<p><b>Please Note:</b> Prices mentioned above are indicative and subject to change.</p>

<p></p><h3>How can Justdial help you find the best packers and movers nearby?</h3><p></p>
<p> Information about experienced and professional ‘packers and movers near me’ can easily be accessed on Justdial according to your preferences. Get details such as address and contact number, hours of operation, services offered, etc. Use filters like location, distance, popularity, etc. to narrow the search results as per the specific requirements. Customer ratings and reviews can help you differentiate the quality of services provided by various packers and movers and accordingly make a well-researched decision. </p>

<p></p><h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemtype="https://schema.org/FAQPage">

<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">1. Are packers and movers in Pune  operating during the present scenario of Covid-19 pandemic?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>Yes, they are operating in areas that they are allowed to and within timings that they are allowed. However, some packers and movers in areas with high concentration of outbreaks may be temporarily closed or operating in different hours.</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>




<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">2. Will packers and movers in Pune provide services for inter-city?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>Some packers and movers provide the service for different cities. It is best to contact the packer and movers in question and inquire to know more.</p>

</div>

</div>

</div>


<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">3. Will packers and movers provide the services of dismantling and installing electronic goods like AC, geyser, etc.?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>No, most packers and movers will not provide this service. To have electronic goods re-installed at your new location, you will have to hire a technician. Some packers and movers may provide you the added services of such technicians which you can find about by inquiring with them.</p>

</div>
	
</div>

</div>


<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">4. What are the charges of packers and movers in Pune?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>The cost depends on the size of the house and the shifting distance. Depending on the distance, charges are approximately:</p>
<p>Rs. 3,000 –Rs. 10,500 for 1 BHK houses</p>
<p>Rs. 8,000 - Rs. 20,500 for 4BHK houses</p>
<p>Office shifting will cost approximately Rs. 6,500 to Rs. 35,000 depending on the distance for local shifting.</p>
<p>For different city, the charges are approximately Rs. 6000 - Rs. 24,000 for 1 BHK</p>
<p>Rs. 18,000 - Rs. 48,000 for 5 BHK.</p>
<p>Office shifting charges to a different city is in the range of Rs. 11,000 to Rs. 40,000.</p>
<p>The services shifting to a different city by packers and movers will also charge you for vehicle transportation charges and more.</p>
	
</div>

</div>

</div>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">5. Will packers and movers provide moving insurance?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>Yes, usually two different types of moving insurance are provided by Packers and movers. Goods transit insurance will cover the damages that happen anyhow in transit. All-inclusive insurance will cover the risks of damages of goods during the entire process of shifting. You can contact the packers and movers to know about their charges for moving insurance.</p>
	
</div>

</div>

</div>


<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">6. Will all goods be covered by moving insurance?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>Packers and movers will provide insurance against damages for most household items. The goods not covered by insurance are valuables, cash, antiques, collectables, documents, fine art, glassware, heirlooms, jewellery, medications, sport memorabilia, and perishable items. You should contact the packers and movers to know more about the coverage of their moving insurance.</p>
	
</div>

</div>

</div>


<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">7. What are the different factors that influence the charges of packers and movers?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>They are Packing charge, Labour charge, Transport charge, Unpacking charge and other charges &amp; expenses like insurance , GST, toll tax, octroy and more. Other factors like total distance from source to destination, size of apartment, total volume and weight of items, size and type of truck/vehicle, quantity and types of packing materials &amp; moving boxes, the number floor of buildings at source &amp; destination, difficulty and time consumption in the process, brand value of packers and movers and experience of moving crew.</p>
	
</div>

</div>

</div>


<div itemscope="" itemprop="mainEntity" itemtype="https://schema.org/Question">

<p></p><h3 itemprop="name">8. What are the GST charges for availing the services of packers and movers?</h3><p></p>

<div itemscope="" itemprop="acceptedAnswer" itemtype="https://schema.org/Answer">

<div itemprop="text">

<p>The GST rate is usually 5% for transportation and 18% for both moving insurance and full-service of packers and movers. You can contact the packers and movers to know about the GST charged for their service.</p>
	
</div>

</div>

</div>


</div>
